divs: Sighting DetailsSeveral triangular shaped ships hovering in the sky. The lights are outlining the shape of a triangle. Not moving. One highly visible under the moon. Beams of light like lines coming from this one under the moon. It is very bright and close. There are 6 others same size with lights hovering in the further distance. Lights changing color but not moving. There are others in the sky but are further away. I know that the government can see these if I can
